{"tha-ap228:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap228:0.2":"Alambanadayakavagga ","tha-ap228:0.3":"6 Ankolapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap228:1.1":"“Narado iti me namam, ","tha-ap228:1.2":"kassapo iti mam vidu; ","tha-ap228:1.3":"Addasam samananaggam, ","tha-ap228:1.4":"vipassim devasakkatam. ","tha-ap228:2.1":"Anubyanjanadharam buddham, ","tha-ap228:2.2":"ahutinam patiggaham; ","tha-ap228:2.3":"Ankolapuppham paggayha, ","tha-ap228:2.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap228:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap228:3.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap228:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap228:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap228:4.1":"Catusattatito kappe, ","tha-ap228:4.2":"romaso nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap228:4.3":"Amukkamalabharano, ","tha-ap228:4.4":"sayoggabalavahano. ","tha-ap228:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap228:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap228:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap228:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ankolapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap228:7.1":"Ankolapupphiyattherassapadanam chattham. "}